Text: (NYSE:AAN) declared a quarterly dividend on Thursday, August 8th, Zacks reports. Investors of record on Thursday, September 19th will be paid a dividend of 0.035 per share on Friday, October 4th. This represents a $0.14 annualized dividend and a yield of 0.22%.
